data.description: Step into a home full of possibilities! This spacious two-story home in the heart of Atascocita has lots of built-ins, custom touches, beautiful living space, plus a 2 car garage! The main floor features a living room with soaring ceilings overlooking the fireplace, oversized primary retreat, kitchen with breakfast area, formal dining room, plus a half bath for guests! Upstairs you'll find spacious secondary bedrooms with connecting bath and a bonus space, perfect for an office/study area!
